TopicTitle: Gaelic Space Program- a let's play

Articles.Content:
Hey all!

 

I just started a new career mode series with the Galileo Planet Pack (which is great because my dog is named Galileo). The first two videos are up on youtube, and I hope you guys will check it out!

We don't get too far yet, but I plan to explore all the planets and moons in the planet pack and get up to some interesting missions and maybe even some livestreams in the future. See you all there!
